content.article_body: ISLAMABAD, Aug 07 (APP):The National Assembly session continued on Thursday at 11:15 a.m. under the chairmanship of Speaker Sardar Ayaz Sadiq at the Parliament House. It marked the third sitting of the ongoing session, with the House set to take up various items from the legislative agenda.
